            <img src="https://legalx24.com/img/loan-recovery.jpg" alt="Loan Recovery Cases" class="w-full h-[200px] object-cover rounded-[16px] mb-4 bg-slate-100" data-themekey="#"/> 
            <h5 class="font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-2">Loan Recovery Cases</h5>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-7 text-[15px]"> Loan recovery matters relate to enforcement of repayment obligations by banks or financial institutions against borrowers in default, strictly as per statutory recovery procedures. </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-7 text-[15px] mt-2"> We assist lenders in filing and pursuing recovery proceedings before civil courts, Debt Recovery Tribunals, and other authorised forums, ensuring proper documentation and lawful enforcement of securities. </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-7 text-[15px] mt-2"> We also help borrowers respond to recovery notices, negotiate workable settlements, restructure repayment terms where possible, and protect their legal rights against irregular recovery action. </p>
         </div>
