            <h5 class="font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-2">DRT &amp; SARFAESI Matters</h5>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-7 text-[15px]"> DRT proceedings and SARFAESI actions deal with recovery of secured debts through statutory powers available to banks and financial institutions against defaulting borrowers. </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-7 text-[15px] mt-2"> We support lenders in issuing demand notices, taking possession in accordance with law, conducting auctions, and completing recovery procedures within the statutory framework. </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-7 text-[15px] mt-2"> We also represent borrowers in challenging improper SARFAESI steps, filing securitisation applications, and pursuing remedies before DRT or appellate forums. </p>
         </div>
         <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-[22px] border-l-[6px] border-emerald-600 shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-2xl transition h-full"> 
