            <h5 class="font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-2">Insolvency &amp; Bankruptcy (IBC)</h5>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-7 text-[15px]"> The Insolvency and Bankruptcy Code provides a formal process for resolving insolvency of companies and individuals within defined timelines under supervision of the tribunal. </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-7 text-[15px] mt-2"> We represent financial creditors, operational creditors, corporate debtors, and professionals before NCLT and NCLAT in insolvency and resolution proceedings. </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-7 text-[15px] mt-2"> Our work includes preparing and filing applications, defending insolvency petitions, advising during resolution processes, and guiding clients through liquidation or recovery stages as required. </p>
