            <h5 class="font-bold text-emerald-900 mb-2">Banking Disputes</h5>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-7 text-[15px]"> Banking disputes may involve unauthorised debits, disputed transactions, unfair recovery action, restructuring disagreements, or breach of banking terms by either side. </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-7 text-[15px] mt-2"> We assist clients in resolving such matters through negotiation, regulatory complaints, tribunal or court proceedings, and other legally recognised dispute resolution methods. </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-7 text-[15px] mt-2"> Our focus remains on protecting the client’s financial position, ensuring compliance with applicable rules, and reaching a timely and workable resolution. </p>
